benak.tomas.crimemonitor.service

Class CrimeService.MaxCrimeIndexInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.service.CrimeService.MaxCrimeIndexInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    CrimeService

    private class CrimeService.MaxCrimeIndexInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used as a holder for the maximum crimes per capita information.

    The maximum crimes per capita value is represented as a pair of integers. The first one is the number of the committed crimes c. The second one is the number of the inhabitants i. The crimes per capita value is defined as (c / i).

    Author:
    Tom
